Peking Application Server Experiment: README
========================================================================
$Id$


Note
----
This experiments work only if the patches from RFC #0071 are applied!
See http://xp-framework.net/rfc/0071 for details and to download the 
patch!


Getting started
---------------
Type the following command line:
$ php server.php 127.0.0.1
  
This will start the peking application server.

Now verify everything works by running:
$ unittest -c net.xp_framework.unittest.remote.RoundtripTest -a 127.0.0.1

